                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13396539" author="davsclaus" created="Tue, 19 Jun 2012 06:15:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You need to enable the shareUnitOfWork option on the recipient list EIP&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13396544" author="davsclaus" created="Tue, 19 Jun 2012 06:27:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is working as designed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In Camel 3.0 the message history EIP is to be refactored, and in this line of work, we should make the shareUnitOfWork / useOriginalMessage a bit more simpler to configure/use. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And maybe change default settings. As for the recipient list it would be more natural to have shareUnitOfWork enabled by default.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See this unit test, how to make this work for you.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1351583&amp;amp;view=rev&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1351583&amp;amp;view=rev&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13398253" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 21 Jun 2012 07:33:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added a FAQ&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=27850079&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=27850079&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
